==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Physicist
<hw>Phys"i*cist</hw> <pr>(f⟦icr⟧z"⟦icr⟧*s⟦icr⟧st)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>One versed in physics.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>A believer in the theory that the
fundamental phenomena of life are to be explained upon purely chemical
and physical principles; -- opposed to <xex>vitalist</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Physicking</ent>⟦br⟧
